<ab><expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> und <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von
                        Ryeden und <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> von
                            <expan>Stetemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> und
                        Peter, uns hat fürgelegt Wolfell <expan>Verb<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, wie daz dem Chunczen Sachsen von
                        Wochendorff, seinem armman, czwey pferd genomen <add>sein
                                    <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan></add> und daz das die ewren getan
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add>süllen</add>, als man im gesagt hab. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>,
                        ob dem also sey, daz ir <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>schicke<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet, daz dem
                            <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan>
<expan>armenman<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> seine
                        pferde <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>werde<ex>n</ex></expan>, als etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
